snippet: Attendance has nearly tripled at Jacksonville’s Museum of Contemporary Art since the City Council president, Clay Yarborough, last week denounced as pornographic a photograph showing a nude pregnant woman reclining on a love-seat.
lead_paragraph: Attendance has nearly tripled at Jacksonville’s Museum of Contemporary Art since the City Council president, Clay Yarborough, last week denounced as pornographic a photograph showing a nude pregnant woman reclining on a love-seat.
